'''瓏·薛爾菲格'''（{{lang-da|Lone Scherfig}}，{{bd|1959年|5月2日}}）是一位[[丹麥|丹麥]]電影女導演與編劇，她曾是激進電影美學運動[[道格玛95|逗馬95宣言]]的參與者，2001年她依照逗馬95宣言拍出來的《{{link-da|戀愛學分保證班|Italiensk for begyndere}}》於[[第51屆柏林影展|第51屆柏林影展]]獲得評審團獎與[[國際影評人協會|費比西國際影評人獎]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tributemovies.com/people/Lone+Scherfig/8495/ |title=Lone Scherfig Biography |publisher=Tributemovies.com |date=1959-05-02 |accessdate=2012-05-18 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125105824/https://www.tributemovies.com/people/Lone+Scherfig/8495/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Roger |last=Ebert |url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20020201/REVIEWS/202010303/1023 |title=Italian For Beginners |publisher=Chicago Suntimes.com |date=2001-02-01 |accessdate=2012-05-18 |archive-date=2012-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121117020249/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20020201%2FREVIEWS%2F202010303%2F1023 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Farmer, Lucy {{cite web|url= http://www.moreintelligentlife.com/blog/lucy-farmer/qa-lone-scherfig-filmmaker|title= THE Q&A: LONE SCHERFIG, FILMMAKER|publisher= ''MoreIntelligentLife.com''|accessdate= 15 February 2010|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100102154337/http://moreintelligentlife.com/blog/lucy-farmer/qa-lone-scherfig-filmmaker|archivedate= 2010年1月2日}}</ref>；後來她漸轉往英語電影圈發展，2009年以《[[成长教育|名媛教育]]》廣受好評，於[[第82屆奧斯卡金像獎|第82屆奧斯卡金像獎]]入圍3個獎項，包括最佳影片。

2019年，她執導的英語片《{{link-en|紐約茶館|The Kindness of Strangers (film)}}》被選為[[第69屆柏林影展|第69屆柏林影展]]開幕片。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.screendaily.com/news/lone-scherfigs-the-kindness-of-strangers-to-open-2019-berlin-film-festival/5135078.article|title=Lone Scherfig's 'The Kindness Of Strangers' to open 2019 Berlin Film Festival|work=Screen Daily|date=2018-12-06|language=en|accessdate=2019-03-17|archive-date=2018-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181207133232/https://www.screendaily.com/news/lone-scherfigs-the-kindness-of-strangers-to-open-2019-berlin-film-festival/5135078.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>

